Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.52,0:00:14.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Never before in all the world had such a mysterious phantom manifested...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.90,0:00:20.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And whenever that strange figure appeared before people,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.83,0:00:25.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,they all felt a chill run down their spines...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.50,0:00:28.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're out of places to run, serial jewelry thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.99,0:00:31.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Villain! Surrender!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.00,0:00:38.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fools! You really believe you can capture me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.68,0:00:41.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.64,0:00:43.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,An invisible person!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.50,0:00:46.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, be shocked! And cringe in fear!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.20,0:00:48.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my true form!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.18,0:00:54.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Was there ever anything more fearsome in this world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.60,0:00:57.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,than this absolute hollowness, this infinite nothingness?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.24,0:01:02.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,To the people involved, it was like glimpsing a rip in the fabric of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.58,0:01:06.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They shivered in terror, shaken to their very souls...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.42,0:01:17.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...she said."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.10,0:01:20.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh... So this is the kind of story Lucy writes...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.96,0:01:22.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.31,0:01:24.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I never said you could read it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.56,0:01:26.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.07,0:01:29.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So this time it's a story about an invisible person, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.35,0:01:34.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, I thought I'd try tackling sort of a different genre, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.10,0:01:37.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody's thought at least once about what would happen
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.37,0:01:39.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,if they became invisible, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.88,0:01:43.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And I had a feeling I could write an interesting story about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.13,0:01:51.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fools! You really believe you can capture me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.04,0:01:55.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, be shocked! And cringe in fear!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.08,0:01:58.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my true form!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.52,0:02:02.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! Stop it! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.67,0:03:37.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you two come here for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.80,0:03:39.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you've got no reason, then get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.69,0:03:42.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're here to invite you out on a job!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.03,0:03:44.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't work, you're gonna be flat broke.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.57,0:03:46.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm busy right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.70,0:03:49.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you two can handle whatever the job is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.62,0:03:53.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the way it works. We're a team, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.59,0:03:54.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.50,0:03:57.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And when we work together as a team, it's gotta include you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.99,0:04:01.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.40,0:04:04.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, I'm starving!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.09,0:04:06.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have anything to eat around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.01,0:04:06.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.79,0:04:10.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't a restaurant!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.31,0:04:14.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Terror of Invisible Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.44,0:04:23.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I lost all my concentration!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.99,0:04:26.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Think I'll clear my head with a bath...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.59,0:04:30.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic ointment...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.39,0:04:37.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right. I prepared it myself, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.22,0:04:41.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Using this will make my skin so beautiful, it'll almost be translucent.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.95,0:04:44.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a long time, maybe I'll put some on...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.74,0:04:59.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,An invisible person...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.44,0:05:03.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what I could do if that really happened to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.03,0:05:05.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Surprise everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.05,0:05:07.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And maybe it would be useful for work...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.32,0:05:08.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What a dreamer!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.46,0:05:18.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Feel a little dizzy...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.34,0:05:20.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.57,0:05:23.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.09,0:05:24.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've really become invisible!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.67,0:05:30.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... I made this ointment seven years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.56,0:05:35.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe is got so old that the effect has changed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.72,0:05:38.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't just stay like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.23,0:05:40.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I need Natsu and the rest to help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.82,0:05:46.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad... If I go outside like this, it'll cause a panic!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.09,0:05:52.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.92,0:05:55.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's strange. No one's there, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.78,0:06:06.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No one can see me, so I'd better be careful or they'll bump into me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.28,0:06:09.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I know. I'll stay off to the side.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.17,0:06:16.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I came out in a hurry, but now that I think of it, I'm naked.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.71,0:06:19.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If the ointment wears off...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.31,0:06:22.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...will happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.60,0:06:27.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Although come to think of it, now that nobody can see me,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.29,0:06:29.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,even if I do this weird pose...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.22,0:06:33.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Or this pose... or this pose...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.25,0:06:35.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody can see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.38,0:06:37.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's embarrassing, but fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.89,0:06:41.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Though I feel like an idiot getting excited all by myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.42,0:06:47.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... Cut it out! Shoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.57,0:06:50.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? There's nothing there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.37,0:06:58.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whose voice is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.33,0:07:03.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.09,0:07:05.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd better get to Fairy Tail and fast...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.08,0:07:08.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that? Something's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.97,0:07:10.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Weird!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.39,0:07:12.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right! I feel something!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.45,0:07:14.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's soft and warm!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.30,0:07:15.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels like a person!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.89,0:07:17.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.68,0:07:23.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That tickles! Knock it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.63,0:07:25.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.83,0:07:28.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It ran away!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.90,0:07:31.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.43,0:07:34.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an invisible ghost!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.08,0:07:35.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's catch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.30,0:07:38.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gimme a break! What a revolting development!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.06,0:07:41.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know! I'll hide in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.98,0:07:45.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.08,0:07:49.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Safe...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.48,0:07:59.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,F-Finally made it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.12,0:08:02.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What a mooch, Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.39,0:08:06.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, so Lucy-nee literally booted you out?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.78,0:08:11.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, even though I was there to invite her out on a job!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.27,0:08:13.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's only natural she'd be angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.30,0:08:17.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear you two sometimes even use her bath without asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.41,0:08:19.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a flagrant breach of manners.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.98,0:08:21.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.82,0:08:24.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though you're on the same team, a line needs to be drawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.91,0:08:29.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever you're out of money, come over here and I'll feed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.53,0:08:32.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Although for inconsiderate jerks like you two,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.68,0:08:34.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure this goes right over your heads.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.20,0:08:38.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I think she could've been a little nicer to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.43,0:08:42.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That kind of behavior is the reason she'll never be able to snag a boyfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.08,0:08:44.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's got her number!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.76,0:08:49.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Or even if she got a boyfriend, I bet he'd run away first chance he had.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.08,0:08:52.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She was born a "lady" outside, but she's a barbarian on the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.57,0:08:57.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mm. Only a Man who was truly wild could be a match for her.  {"savage" or "rough" better?}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.56,0:09:02.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy should learn a little from Team Shadow Gear's Levy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.05,0:09:04.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She should act more like a lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.38,0:09:08.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not all that ladylike myself, but still...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.06,0:09:14.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm the butt of their jokes when they think I'm not here...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.34,0:09:20.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard! What the hell'd you do that for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.21,0:09:22.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hah? What the hell are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.20,0:09:26.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't play dumb! You just doused me with a mug of booze!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.72,0:09:28.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go making weird accusations!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.18,0:09:31.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If it wasn't you, then who did it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.10,0:09:32.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How do I know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.84,0:09:33.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.49,0:09:36.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.29,0:09:39.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one that started it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.14,0:09:42.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What have we here?! A fight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.60,0:09:44.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.82,0:09:47.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Something about getting splashed with booze...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.82,0:09:53.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! If you're gonna fight, take it elsewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.64,0:09:59.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just when I was getting into it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.68,0:10:05.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you doin'?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.14,0:10:08.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Asshole! You lookin' for a fight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.79,0:10:10.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't bug me when I'm eatin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.46,0:10:13.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hah?! I don't know what the hell you're talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.53,0:10:15.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.68,0:10:17.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Move it! We're tryin' to have a fight here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.47,0:10:20.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Seven years have passed and you still haven't picked a job?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.71,0:10:23.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking for the job that only I can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.90,0:10:36.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.09,0:10:39.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, calm down! What started this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.02,0:10:42.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave them be. This is no different than usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.05,0:10:45.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But at this rate, they'll destroy the guild hall!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.72,0:10:47.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We can always fix it later.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.99,0:10:51.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not getting upset by every little thing is the mark of an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.22,0:10:54.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, this bunch hasn't matured at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.82,0:10:57.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If anything, they've become even more boisterous these past seven years...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.16,0:11:04.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Morons... You've taken it too far!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.34,0:11:07.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even Erza-san joined in!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.27,0:11:10.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I figured she would...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.37,0:11:14.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like Erza hasn't matured any either.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.94,0:11:19.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's become a regular riot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.29,0:11:23.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.38,0:11:28.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy's... voice? And her scent, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.12,0:11:34.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy, is that you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.09,0:11:37.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch me there!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.87,0:11:43.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy, he says?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.20,0:11:46.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy's here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.03,0:11:47.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I could hear her voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.57,0:11:48.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't see her!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.16,0:11:50.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.09,0:11:56.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The cat's out of the bag!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.33,0:12:09.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So that's what happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.66,0:12:12.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What a weird sight...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.16,0:12:16.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Stop staring at me like that. I'm getting embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.40,0:12:17.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Creepy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.50,0:12:18.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's creepy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.78,0:12:20.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a real pickle...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.80,0:12:24.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For now, we rounded up some clothes for you, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.64,0:12:26.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't change back to normal?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.89,0:12:30.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No... I came here because I thought you guys could do something...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.81,0:12:34.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see what the problem is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.37,0:12:37.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It could be a lot of fun, so let's go out on a job with you like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.42,0:12:39.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't go like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.49,0:12:43.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't anyone know of a way to cancel out invisibility magic?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.65,0:12:45.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Easier said than done...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.81,0:12:47.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.94,0:12:49.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! I have a good idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.84,0:12:50.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.80,0:12:54.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Toasting you with flames will probably fix it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.16,0:12:57.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You have grounds to believe that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.47,0:13:01.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,True, when I turned to stone that one time, he did the same thing to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.79,0:13:05.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But if we can't think of anything else, I guess that's the only way to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.66,0:13:09.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mm. If you're a Man, you'll do it without hesitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.25,0:13:12.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.35,0:13:15.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, here I go, Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.07,0:13:16.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help you, Natsu-nii!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.56,0:13:19.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! I'm not mentally prepared yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.64,0:13:21.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready... go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.23,0:13:24.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hot-hot-hot-hot-hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.57,0:13:27.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, looks like it didn't work...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.97,0:13:29.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course it didn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.20,0:13:33.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep your chin up, Lu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.19,0:13:34.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure we'll find a way...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.96,0:13:38.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oui. I believe a time like this is made for me to step up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.26,0:13:39.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Reedus!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.68,0:13:41.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have some kind of plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.79,0:13:43.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.59,0:13:46.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All I have to do is paint Lucy's face!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.26,0:13:54.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That looks like her and doesn't look like her at the same time...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.17,0:13:56.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike the real Lucy, she's beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.19,0:14:00.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I kind of have mixed feelings...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.55,0:14:03.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm... Then what if I add this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.57,0:14:05.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now this, I hate!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.10,0:14:07.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can paint better than that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.12,0:14:07.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.51,0:14:10.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Finished! Looks just like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.95,0:14:12.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.66,0:14:16.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! Lucy's face is more like this, this, and like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.88,0:14:18.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, her eyes are more like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.48,0:14:21.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.08,0:14:22.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.05,0:14:23.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, "mmm"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.92,0:14:27.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't her nose and mouth like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.97,0:14:31.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, there's more of an impact if we go like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.62,0:14:34.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys suck. Let me give it a whack!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.54,0:14:36.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.21,0:14:39.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I used to take drawing class when I was a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.18,0:14:41.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I would go bolder, like so!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.61,0:14:43.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's important to have distinct characteristics.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.56,0:14:46.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a girl, so we should make her cuter!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.72,0:14:48.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She needs sparkling eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.32,0:14:51.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Or better yet, how about black hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.04,0:14:52.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It may look good on her!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.93,0:14:55.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather try out a different hairstyle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.85,0:14:57.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Like very short or with dreads...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.70,0:15:00.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She'd look good with an afro, too, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.45,0:15:02.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we have to paint her face, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.11,0:15:06.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My face isn't a toy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.24,0:15:08.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, she's a Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.50,0:15:10.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd you make me like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.20,0:15:12.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a pain! Leave everything to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.34,0:15:15.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, that looks just like her!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.10,0:15:17.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you have no complaints about this, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.69,0:15:23.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Creepy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.80,0:15:25.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.81,0:15:28.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.27,0:15:31.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A photo from when they did an article on us that time...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.38,0:15:34.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For now, make do with that, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.07,0:15:37.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this is better than before, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.45,0:15:39.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You think so...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.54,0:15:41.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.57,0:15:43.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you two go?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.72,0:15:45.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.17,0:15:48.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We picked up the bottle of ointment and her Celestial Keys.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.15,0:15:52.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see! I can ask my Celestial Spirits for help!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.33,0:15:54.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Wendy and Carla!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.79,0:15:57.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But which Spirit should I summon?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.67,0:16:02.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I could count on Loke or Aquarius at a time like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.30,0:16:04.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy, call out Gemini.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.86,0:16:07.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gemini? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.27,0:16:11.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They can transform into you. Just try it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.07,0:16:15.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay. Gate of the Twins, I open thee! Gemini!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.15,0:16:19.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Long time no see! Gemini here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.37,0:16:21.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.28,0:16:23.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks exactly like Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.10,0:16:24.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Gemini for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.33,0:16:27.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So... let's do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.82,0:16:32.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Lucy! Everyone, please be my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.35,0:16:34.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We can keep this up forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.76,0:16:37.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it! Nice idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.43,0:16:39.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This doesn't solve anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.39,0:16:42.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, that's the spitting image of her...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.55,0:16:45.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh! I transform into an exact duplicate.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.66,0:16:48.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can even copy memories and abilities!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.40,0:16:52.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, why don't we just say this is the real thing from now on?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.58,0:16:55.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. After all, the looks and powers are the same...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.33,0:16:59.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If anything, this one seems more mild-mannered and easier to get along with...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.04,0:17:00.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.48,0:17:02.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kidding! Only kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.01,0:17:04.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fried and Levy, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.31,0:17:07.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Analyzing the formulation of the recipe...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.75,0:17:10.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If we find out the makeup of the magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.11,0:17:12.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,there may be Runes that can cancel it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.09,0:17:14.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got it analyzed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.02,0:17:17.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fried, these are the ointment's ingredients.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.53,0:17:20.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave the rest to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.89,0:17:27.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The effects of a magical ointment will be dispelled...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.54,0:17:30.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...for whoever is in these Runes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.63,0:17:38.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, can you see anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.97,0:17:40.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.36,0:17:42.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that really work?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.24,0:17:42.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It does.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.16,0:17:47.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,However, the ointment was sitting for seven years...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.00,0:17:49.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So it'll take seven years to be dispelled.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.17,0:17:52.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait that long!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.23,0:17:53.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry, Lu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.47,0:17:59.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's so funny, Lucy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.00,0:18:01.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm crying! Because this is hopeless!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.52,0:18:08.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this? Not only my body, but now the clothes are becoming invisible?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.80,0:18:11.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your whole existence is starting to disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.18,0:18:12.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What does that mean, Levy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.98,0:18:15.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not just Lu-chan becoming invisible,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.28,0:18:17.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but she's actually starting to vanish!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.86,0:18:23.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that, it will be as if she never existed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.78,0:18:25.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The bottle disappeared?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.34,0:18:30.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Since it'll be as if Lucy never existed, then her things will vanish, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.63,0:18:33.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet her room is empty by now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.79,0:18:47.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I don't want this to happen! I don't want it so I never existed!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.47,0:18:49.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.92,0:18:51.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If I do this...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.28,0:18:59.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What was I just saying...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.02,0:19:01.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know... Probably about work...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.95,0:19:06.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I was painting something... but what was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.40,0:19:10.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like someone was standing right here just a second ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.71,0:19:13.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have the same feeling. Strange, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.58,0:19:16.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel weird, like something is missing...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.97,0:19:19.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too... Is it just our imaginations?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.54,0:19:21.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you feel like that too, Natsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.19,0:19:24.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.07,0:19:26.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I dunno!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.10,0:19:28.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.23,0:19:30.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, have you forgotten about me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.38,0:19:33.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, well. Let's get to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.99,0:19:37.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fried, sit down. I'm not done painting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.61,0:19:40.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... What kind of job would I be able to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.48,0:19:38.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.44,0:19:43.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu! I'm here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.42,0:19:46.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray! Can't you hear me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.10,0:19:49.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza! Happy! Wendy! Carla!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.76,0:19:51.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.71,0:19:57.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use. None of them can hear me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.25,0:20:00.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's forgotten me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.85,0:20:03.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I never existed...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.51,0:20:07.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then it's just like I'm a ghost!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.18,0:20:11.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna be a ghost!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.48,0:20:24.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! What do you say we go to work?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.88,0:20:26.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy! Lucy! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.98,0:20:28.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.66,0:20:32.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.59,0:20:35.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.91,0:20:39.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.61,0:20:42.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Our friend! Our teammate!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.92,0:20:44.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.70,0:20:45.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy was here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.84,0:20:47.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.21,0:20:48.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.74,0:20:58.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu... Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.58,0:21:00.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The magic was dispelled!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.15,0:21:05.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe the effect of the ointment was nullified when Natsu remembered her!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.99,0:21:08.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, could be.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.37,0:21:12.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, like they say, magic takes heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.12,0:21:14.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And whether it's a little magic or a lot,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.93,0:21:16.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,nothin' can break the bond of the guild!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.67,0:21:23.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You talk a good game, but the three of you didn't do a thing to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.43,0:21:26.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.07,0:21:29.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When we go to work as a team, it's just gotta include you, Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.96,0:21:30.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.39,0:21:37.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, it was kind of fun being invisible,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.72,0:21:41.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but it was way too lonely when my friends didn't notice I was there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.82,0:21:48.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't always count on them, but they're all my dear friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.52,0:21:52.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna get rid of this quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.99,0:21:55.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad you're back, Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.59,0:22:10.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.23,0:22:12.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.49,0:22:13.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.64,0:22:15.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd my face go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.57,0:22:16.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.60,0:22:18.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me! Who the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.53,0:22:23.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I do wish everyone was a little more level-headed...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.20,0:23:58.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, have you seen Elfman?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.23,0:24:00.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He went out on an errand for Mira.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.16,0:24:03.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I had a little brother, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.52,0:24:04.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hah? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.50,0:24:06.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So I could send him out shopping for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.97,0:24:08.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and carry my things for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.80,0:24:14.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and on top of that, I'd get the right to have one more fish than him!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.02,0:24:16.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: Father's Memento.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.63,0:24:20.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that how you see those two?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.26,0:24:22.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.14,0:24:23.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your mind is too warped, Happy...
